<div type="edition" xml:lang="und" rendition="class:grantha maturity:vernacular">

<p>On the top row are engraved the figures respectively of Sun, Flywhisk, Lamp, Flywhisk, and crescent.</p>

<p>The second row has the figures Lamp-stand, Pot on tripod, Flagstaff(?), Fish, Pot on tripod.</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> samasta jagadādhāra sō</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">makulatilaka madhurāpurimādhava</hi>
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha">kēraḷavamśa nirmūlana laṅkādvi</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">paluṇṭana dvi<unclear>ti</unclear>yarāma pōḷa</hi>
<lb n="5" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">kulaśaila<unclear>ku</unclear>liśa karṇāṭarāja</hi>
<lb n="6" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">vidrāvaṇa kāṅka karikūṭapākala</hi>
<lb n="7"/><hi rend="grantha">vividha ripudurga<unclear>ma</unclear>rdana viragaṇḍa gō</hi>
<lb n="8" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">pāla vipinadāvadahana kāñcipura</hi>
<lb n="9" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">varādhiśvara gaṇapati hariṇaśā</hi>
<lb n="10"/><hi rend="grantha">rdūla nēl</hi><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">l</seg><hi rend="grantha">ūrupura piracita pirābhi</hi>
<lb n="11" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">ṣēka praṇatarāja pratiṣṭāpaka</hi>
<lb n="12"/><hi rend="grantha">mahārājādhirāja</hi>
<lb n="13"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī sundara pāṇḍya <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> </hi>
<lb n="14"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">kulottuṅka <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> </seg>
<lb n="15"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">ṭaiyāṟkku tiṅkaḷ <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> </seg>
<lb n="16"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">ṟāṉa <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> </seg>
<lb n="17"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">maṇaṉūrum <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> </seg>
<lb n="18"/><hi rend="grantha">sarva</hi><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">mā</seg><hi rend="grantha">nnya <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> </hi>
<lb n="19"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">yākavum Ivvūr <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> </seg>
<lb n="20"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">tiruviṭai <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> pacāṉamutal</seg>
<lb n="21"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">pūjaiyum tiruppaṇiyum <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> </seg>
<lb n="22"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">Ippaṭikku Iva <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> </seg>
<lb n="23-29"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> </seg>
<lb n="30"/><hi rend="grantha">sundarapāṇḍya dēvabhaṭṭā <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> tē</hi>
<lb n="31"/><hi rend="grantha">rastāsana niṣēvaṇōsura <gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> yat kurvanti</hi> 
<lb n="32"/><hi rend="grantha">kōlāhalam bhṛṅgārōma <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> cāmaram mahaḷā</hi>
<lb n="33" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ruḥ kaḷācima <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> ḷacōḷa</hi>
<lb n="34"/><hi rend="grantha">hē <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ḷa bhujāma <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> purā śrāṇavaḥ Apatu</hi>
<lb n="35"/><hi rend="grantha">tiru <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> mēghakānti rūpa</hi>
<lb n="36"/><hi rend="grantha"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> dharitrīmmāyuga kṛpāṇadviṣa</hi>
<lb n="37" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">davanipatinā <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> mabhyēti vṛdthim vasati</hi>
<lb n="38" break="no"/><seg xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> panā</seg> <hi rend="grantha">rājiryasya dhārājvalan <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi>
</p>

